{
  "stem": "23645.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So of course, I had all these-- all this-- my face, I couldn't see out of my eyes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember thinking, when they take one look at me with all-- all the-- these huge openings, the sores on my-- on my face, I'll be marked for dead immediately.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And really-- I thought that this is going to really, after all these years, and this is getting close, I'm going to make it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I thought, I won't survive that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a Gestapo man with a stick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as I went right up to the neck, and he pushed me right on there, just completely down, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I came out, I-- I-- I just had to do this, and it hurt like hell.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this thing just-- I thought I was going to die right then and there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But what I didn't know is that it was a disinfectant, and the sores healed in no time afterwards, and I was fine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was just a miracle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I went into Block 8, which, again, was political, truly political, and there were very few Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Another friend of mine that is on that picture I showed you, Abraham Chopnik, we shared a bunk together and became very, very close friends.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He lives in New York now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I think he was telling me that he was going to do this as well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then my life in Buchenwald was actually the easiest on me from all the camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Yet [INAUDIBLE] and all these other ones are not known that much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But the-- the agony there was just horrendous.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
